Vyongeye, igihe abanyeshure bariko barashira ku muhora wo kuri Internet, barahaseruka ngo bacike ibiterasoni ku bijanye n’isi ibakikuje, kubera ko bakeneye kugaburira abantu bashimishwa n’ivyo bariko barigisha, biratuma abanyeshure baba abanyabwenge n’abashimishije (Toto, 2004).
